issue.title: Updated Kanna to Swift 4.
issue.body:
I couldn't get the app to build in Xcode Version 9.0 (9A235) when checking it out and running `pod install`. Lots of issues with Kanna, so I pointed to the Swift 4 branch and made a few small updates.

Let me know if this builds with your configuration, I made sure not to check in any project or /Pods changes, just the `Podfile`, `Podfile.lock`, and `Pods/Manifest.lock` since they were checked into this repo.
